# Affiliate automation (unofficial)

- Assume automation is brittle (layout changes/CAPTCHA/rate limits). Build for failure.
- Every automated path must have:
  - **Per-service enable/disable** and an automation **kill switch**
  - Job **observability** (status, attempts, timestamps, last error)
  - Artifacts (screenshot/trace) with redaction where needed
  - A **manual fallback** path; admin can mark manual success
- Manual success proof is **tiered by service value/risk** and is **internal-only**.
- Sync jobs (reference pricing) run **daily** by default + **manual on-demand**, with progress tracking and “notify on change”.

